<function>

access:   public

name: addFilter

param: string, $name

param: string, $method

return: void

</function>

Adds a pre-filter for an element

* Parameters:

 * string //$name//: The element name.

 * string //$method//: Solar_Filter method or PHP function to use for filtering.

* Returns void

Adds a pre-filter for an element

Adds a pre-filter for an element. All pre-filters are applied via 
{@link Solar_Filter::multiple()} and should conform to the 
specifications for that method.